data.title: Licensed Contractors by Business Name July22
data.meta_description: Licensed Contractors by Business Name July22 (1) - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document lists licensed contractors in Ohio by business name, address, name of licensed contractor, license number, and type of license. It includes over 200 entries with businesses licensed for activities like general contracting, plumbing, electrical work, HVAC, roofing and more. The licensed contractors and license information are intended to verify that contractors are properly licensed to conduct business in Ohio.
